<text>
  <chapter>Dhammacakkapavattanadīpanīgāthā</chapter>
  <hangnum nr="174"/>
  <gatha type="1"> Sammāsambodhiñānaṃ hatasakalamalaṃ suddhato cātisuddhaṃ,</gatha>
  <gatha type="2">Addhā laddhā suladdhaṃ vatamiti satataṃ cintayanto subodhiṃ;</gatha>
  <gatha type="3">Sattāhaṃ sattamevaṃ vividhaphalasukhaṃ vitināmesi kālaṃ,</gatha>
  <gatha type="last">Brahmenāyācito so isipatanavane vattayī dhammacakkaṃ.</gatha>
</text>
